name: dying in a bedroom at holiday in express after continental breakfast
description: a tribute to OMGiDRAWEDit. a man walks back to his room with the spoils of a tainted continental breakfast. including a pillow made of raw beef. and a tray of danishes. the staff says he dies of natural causes. and he might have. but the faint glow the of the chili's sign knows secrets. knows the seedy underbelly of this bedroom.
